{"word":"G3753 - ὅτε - hóte - hot'-eh - After","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὅτε</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>hóte"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>hot'-eh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>After"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"போது, பொழுது, பின்பு - எச்சம்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"when"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G3739 - ὅς - hós - hos/3739\">G3739</a> and <a href=\"#/G5037 - τέ - té - teh/5037\">G5037</a>; at <i>which</i> (thing) <i>too</i>, that is, <i>when:</i> - after (that), as soon as, that, when, while. <p/>Second form also feminine, third form also neuter and fourth form simply the article <a href=\"#/G3588 - ὁ - ho - ho/3588\">G3588</a> followed by <a href=\"#/G5037 - τέ - té - teh/5037\">G5037</a>; so written (in some editions) to distinguish them from <a href=\"#/G3752 - ὅταν - hótan - hot'-an/3752\">G3752</a> and <a href=\"#/G5119 - τότε - tóte - tot'-eh/5119\">G5119</a>."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}